    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Welcome to All Nippon Airways.\nWe look forward to serving you and to making your flight\nas comfortable and enjoyable as possible.\nPlease feel free to contact us at any time.\nCiER\n•\nE-=\u003e50-N\nPONL\n471 ALOMba\nexenso\n1€0--7\n= #-\n•\nTOKYO-LOS ANGELES\nLOS ANGELES—TOKYO\ncere\nLUNCH\nAPPETIZERS\nMarinated Salmon Trout\nwith Black Pepper\nSoft Salami\nPotato Salad\nAPPETIZERS\nSmoked Salmon with Lemon\nMarinated Sausage\nHOT ENTREE SELECTION\nBeef \u0026 Chicken \"Teriyaki\"' Style\nHOT ENTREE SELECTION\nSeafood Cardinal Style\nCod with Saffron Sauce\nChicken Cacciatore Style with Lasagna JAPANESE NOODLES\nJAPANESE DELICACIES\nDESSERT\nCHEESE \u0026 CRACKERS\nTABLE ROLL.\nCOFFEE or TEA\nexe\nBREAKFAST\nHOT ENTREE\nFried Calamary Balls\nwith Pickles Sauce\nSEASONAL SALAD\nDESSERT\nMORNING ROLL\nCOFFEE or TEA\nSEASONAL FRUITS\nCHEESE \u0026 CRACKERS\nTABLE ROLL\n•\nCOFFEE or TEA\nexe\nREFRESHMENT\nHOT ENTREE\nShrimp \u0026 Scallop\nwith Hot Pepper Sauce\nSEASONAL SALAD\nDESSERT\nTABLE ROLL\nCOFFEE or TEA\nWe apologize if occasionally your choice is not available.",
      "ANA"
